1.title: A Sexy Country Swap
1.plot: Mary, a former beauty pageant queen, and Jessica, a bride-to-be trapped in an oversize tomboy style, will have a fashion makeover and unbeknown to them will swap clothes for 24 hours.

2.title: A Sporty Flirty Swap
2.plot: Emma is thirty something and trapped in a teeny bop wardrobe whereas Amanda, a high school track and field coach, is obsessed with athletic sportswear. These women will have a fashion makeover and unbeknown to them will swap clothes for 24 hours.

3.title: A Racy Mommy Swap
3.plot: Robyn, a stay-at-home mom who hides her body beneath maternity clothes, and Sheron, a nurse whose attention-seeking clothes enter the room before she does, will swap clothing for 24 hours as part of a makeover process.

4.title: A Girlie Tomboy Swap
4.plot: Dina, a girly girl who doesn't dress down for any occasion, and Allison, a flight instructor with a zero tolerance policy for feminine clothes, will be asked to swap clothes for 24 hours as part of a makeover process.

5.title: A Frumpy Goth Swap
5.plot: Emily, a Goth girl who hides her soft side behind black clothing, and Tanis, who recently lost weight and only wears dresses, will be asked to swap clothes for 24 hours as part of the makeover process.

6.title: A Rocker Granny Swap
6.plot: Josie, a sexy rock singer with an overly risqué daytime look, and Mona, a special education teacher hiding behind her deceased grandmother's dowdy clothes, will be asked to swap clothes for 24 hours as part of a makeover process.

imdb.plot outline: Dare To Wear flips the script on the makeover show construct. Host and style expert Tai Beauchamp asks two extreme fashion disasters on total opposite sides of the style spectrum to switch perspectives by swapping wardrobes. The result is like hitting their own personal style reset button. Not only does this change their outward appearance, but their inner sense of self. After being shocked to learn that they have to swap clothing, these women will spend a day in the other's clothes. The women gain a newfound understanding, and branch out to leave their comfort zone for a head to toe transformation.
